{"tid":1883834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息稱呈陽性反應男子與確診同事曾到醫管局總部開會","createTime":"2020-02-17T08:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T09:13:58.000Z","uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"178b966e9d14f97b116d6632c6e639bae1ef4a9d","tid":1883834,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:29:13.000Z","msg":"消息指，本港再多一人，初步對新型冠狀病毒測試呈陽性反應，病人是一名45歲男子，目前正在伊利沙伯醫院留醫，相信他與昨天住在太古城的54歲確診男子個案有關。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，兩人是同事，日前曾到醫管局總部開會，醫管局已在相關地點進行消毒清洗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509013-20200217.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509013-20200217.htm&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=732da49e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509013-20200217.htm&h=41f26b47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509013-20200217.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5667c4a793e573ceb2796d9e808c1770d0c888c2","tid":1883834,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ym6n7MC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fym6n7MC.jpg&h=a30ed438&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b01086c3ca5fc561c88c716679ad0ae643799d8","tid":1883834,"uid":8170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:44:39.000Z","msg":"最緊要人有事"},{"pid":"ecd412c5e83b9d09bb1d58b3d281bd4123b6c7d7","tid":1883834,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5667c4a793e573ceb2796d9e808c1770d0c888c2","tid":1883834,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ym6n7MC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fym6n7MC.jpg&h=a30ed438&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T09:13: